### Most Useful shorcuts

| Shorcut                          | Action                                            |
| :---                             | :---                                              |
| `Ctrl + Shift + P`<br>`(F1)`     | Display command palette                           |
| `Ctrl + P`                       | Display _search files_ palette                    |
| `Ctrl + Shift + Â´`               | Open terminal                                     |
| `Ctrl + Tab`                     | Navigate between files                            |
| `Ctrl + B`                       | Open / close side bar                             |
| `Ctrl + Shift + E`               | Explorer view                                     |
| `Ctrl + Shift + F `              | Search whole project                              |
| `Ctrl + Shift + G`               | Show git options                                  |
| `Ctrl + Shift + D`               | Show debug options                                |
| `Ctrl + Shift + X`               | Show extensions panel                             |
| <code>CTRL + &#124; </code>      | Split editor                                      |
| `CTRL + W `                      | Close current tab                                 |
| `CTRL + N`<br>`CTRL + Shift + N` | New tab <br> window                               |
| `(F5)`                           | Start debug (Node, VSC Extensions, and .NET Core) |
| `(CTRL + K) + M`                 | Set file language                                 |

